{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-the-css-transform-scale-property-to-scale-an-element-on-hover","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi CSS transform scale svojstvo za uvecanje elementa pri hoveru","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><code>transform</code> svojstvo ima vise funkcija koje vam omogucavaju da uvecate, pomerite, rotirate, izoblicite itd. elemente. Kada se koristi zajedno sa pseudo-klasama kao sto je <code>:hover</code>, koje opisuju odredeno stanje elementa, <code>transform</code> moze poboljsati interaktivnost elemenata.</p>\n<p>Evo primera uvecanja pasus elemenata na 2.1 puta originalne velicine kada korisnik predje misem preko njih:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">p:hover {\n  transform: scale(2.1);\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> Primena transformacije na <code>div</code> element uticace i na sve njegove child elemente.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d78a5367417b2b2512ada","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodajte CSS pravilo za <code>div</code> <code>hover</code> stanje i koristite <code>transform</code> svojstvo da uvecate <code>div</code> element na 1.1 puta originalne velicine kada korisnik predje misem preko njega.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cyLPJuM","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301077,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-the-css-transform-scale-property-to-scale-an-element-on-hover"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  div {\n    width: 70%;\n    height: 100px;\n    margin:  50px auto;\n    background: linear-gradient(\n      53deg,\n      #ccfffc,\n      #ffcccf\n    );\n  }\n\n\n\n</style>\n\n<div></div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Velicina <code>div</code> elementa treba da se uveca za 1.1 puta kada korisnik predje misem preko njega.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /div:hover\\s*?{\\s*?transform:\\s*?scale\\(1\\.1\\);/gi);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#applied-visual-design","dashedName":"use-the-css-transform-scale-property-to-scale-an-element-on-hover","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"applied-visual-design","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-the-css-transform-property-skewx-to-skew-an-element-along-the-x-axis","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-the-css-transform-scale-property-to-change-the-size-of-an-element","id":"587d78a5367417b2b2512ada","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\n  .balls {\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    position: fixed;\n    width: 50px;\n    height: 50px;\n    top: 60%;\n    animation-name: jump;\n    animation-duration: 2s;\n    animation-iteration-count: infinite;\n  }\n  #red {\n    background: red;\n    left: 25%;\n    animation-timing-function: linear;\n  }\n  #blue {\n    background: blue;\n    left: 50%;\n    animation-timing-function: ease-out;\n  }\n  #green {\n    background: green;\n    left: 75%;\n    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.311, 0.441, 0.444, 1.649);\n  }\n\n  @keyframes jump {\n    50% {\n      top: 10%;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"r